{
  "stem": "9725.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't unusual to have more than 20 people on Sunday afternoon to come and to sit in the garden.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, the aunts kept comfortable clothes there, because people were wearing corsets and things like that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they divested themselves of that, and-- and came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the cousins, and so on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and I think it really was-- it must have been, like, extensive psychology.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, everybody brought their problems there, and everything was being hashed and rehashed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I must confess, I always listened to things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they thought that I didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I feel very fortunate that I know of many family things, because I was interested in it, and I wanted to know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they thought I didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a very large extended family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even so, my mother only had one brother who left for Turkey around the time when I was a year or so old.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't see him often, like twice a year, he used to come back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But those uncles and aunts, which were my mother's uncles and aunts, but I called them uncles and aunts, and cousins, and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But coming back to the religious situation, which-- which you wanted to know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- my father went to-- to temple every Saturday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every Friday night and Saturday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so Friday night, we had a large type of thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went, my brother and I, also went to temple every-- every Saturday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were, sort of, children services.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We actually belonged to two temples.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, one was the more conservative one, where my parents were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But from school, we had to attend services which was in a-- well, you couldn't call it reform.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
